title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 30 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 30 2022
description:
Unvaccinated tennis star, Novak Djokovic, out of U.S. Open; can't travel into U.S. Historic Karine Jean-Pierre thinks it's fine that five million illegal immigrants crossed the border, many unvaccinated, during Biden administration. Clay compares that this amount roughly equals the population of that entire state of Alabama. KJP, who C&B state is the worst press secretary in memory, says some illegal immigrants don't just also walk over border; Doocy rightly argues they do, and Clay and Buck agree. Buck reminds us, "The point of the system is to create more Democrat voters." Clay wonders, "What happens if all the Hispanic voters continue to break Republican?" eBay demands tax information for transactions. Mainstream media uses Trump to stimulate the fears of liberals. Newest trend in pets: emotional support alligator. The person it's supporting even sleeps with it!

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
